This is the remnants of an effort to introduce VM introspection in
XenClient/OpenXT. It is not in use and is being mothballed for now.

The additional patches and recipe can be found in the oebits dir.

Most of this is a mirror of another project:

http://www.xenproject.org/directory/directory/projects/79-xenaccess.html
https://code.google.com/archive/p/xenaccess/downloads
